### Variabel Global
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5555

### 1. Cek Status Kesehatan API (Health Check)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Berlangganan Newsletter
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/newsletter
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "warga_cilegon@example.com"
}

###

### 3. Ambil Semua Pelanggan Newsletter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/newsletter
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Pendaftaran Anggota Baru Karang Taruna
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Budi Setiawan",
  "email": "budi.setiawan@example.com",
  "phone": "081234567890",
  "interest": "Seni Budaya",
  "reason": "Ingin berkontribusi memajukan kegiatan pemuda di Kelurahan Rawa Arum."
}

###

### 5. Ambil Semua Pendaftar Anggota
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/register
Accept: application/json

###

### 6. Membuat Pengumuman / Info Baru (Loker, UMKM, Kegiatan)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/info
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Lowongan Kerja Admin Kelurahan",
  "description": "Dibutuhkan tenaga admin harian lepas untuk kelurahan Rawa Arum. Syarat minimal SMA/SMK dan menguasai Ms. Office.",
  "type": "loker",
  "date": "23 Juli 2026",
  "imageUrl": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1486406146926-c627a92ad1ab?q=80&w=400",
  "badge": "Loker",
  "linkText": "Hubungi Kelurahan"
}

###

### 7. Ambil Semua Info (Bisa difilter ?type=loker|umkm|kegiatan|pengumuman)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/info?type=loker
Accept: application/json
